<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to Syllabest, <%= @student.first_name %>!</h1>
    <p>Your professor has signed you into a course on Syllabest. We think Syllabest is great product, and we hope you do too! </p>
    <p>You can check out your syllabus <a href='http://www.syllabest.me/#users/<%= @syllabus.user_id.to_s %>/syllabuses/<%= @syllabus.id.to_s %>'>here</a></p>
    <p>Syllabest is a live syllabus app. We aim to make the barrier of communication lower for professors and students. You will be updated any time your professor makes a change to the syllabus.
    <p>Thanks from everyone at Syllabest. Enjoy!</p>
    <p>-The Syllabest Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
